WEBVTT

00:45.254 --> 00:48.966
PERFECT CROWN

00:59.851 --> 01:01.060
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

01:01.061 --> 01:03.062
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

03:12.567 --> 03:17.280
PERFECT CROWN

03:18.240 --> 03:19.241
An accident?

03:19.741 --> 03:20.991
What have you heard exactly?

03:20.992 --> 03:23.369
Only that there was a collision.

03:27.457 --> 03:28.834
I need to be there.

03:30.669 --> 03:32.086
Do not just stand there.

03:32.087 --> 03:33.712
Prepare to leave at once!

03:33.713 --> 03:34.965
Yes, Your Majesty.

03:37.884 --> 03:43.390
THE ROYAL SEOUL HOSPITAL

03:46.643 --> 03:48.395
How did this happen?

03:48.979 --> 03:50.062
What about His Majesty?

03:50.063 --> 03:52.232
Was there an attack on His Majesty's life?

03:53.567 --> 03:55.192
Say something!

03:55.193 --> 03:56.570
Please calm down, Your Majesty.

04:00.240 --> 04:03.325
His scans reveal no fractures
or internal injuries.

04:03.326 --> 04:05.202
Just some minor bruising.

04:05.203 --> 04:06.455
:cue

04:29.186 --> 04:30.270
And the Grand Prince?

04:30.854 --> 04:32.731
I heard he was at the scene as well.

04:33.482 --> 04:34.900
Is he all right?

04:37.944 --> 04:39.237
He is in surgery.

04:39.946 --> 04:42.449
It appears his left shoulder bore
much of the impact.

04:43.283 --> 04:45.952
It seems he has done everything
in his power to stop the car.

04:47.078 --> 04:48.079
Prime Minister Min.

04:50.207 --> 04:51.208
May I have a word?

05:06.681 --> 05:09.266
Photos of the accident
have spread on social media.

05:09.267 --> 05:10.976
Her conspicuous vehicle didn't help.

05:10.977 --> 05:13.145
How is Ms. Seong doing?

05:13.146 --> 05:16.066
She's still unconscious,
but the scans have come back clean.

05:16.900 --> 05:20.152
Hmm. Are photos of the escort vehicles
also circulating?

05:20.153 --> 05:23.572
No. They were some distance away
from the scene,

05:23.573 --> 05:25.407
and we're removing them as they appear.

05:25.408 --> 05:26.492
That should be enough.

05:26.493 --> 05:27.993
Pushing too hard will raise--

05:27.994 --> 05:29.287
What did you just say?

05:33.166 --> 05:36.127
What does Ms. Seong Huiju
have to do with any of this?

05:42.300 --> 05:44.302
Are you saying the vehicle involved,

05:45.053 --> 05:47.848
the one His Majesty was in,
belongs to that woman?

05:54.729 --> 05:55.730
Your Majesty.

06:00.193 --> 06:01.236
Where are you going?

06:04.489 --> 06:06.658
Must I report such things to you?

06:12.163 --> 06:13.164
The wise decision

06:14.165 --> 06:16.626
would be to not go anywhere.

06:19.462 --> 06:22.090
The people know
Ms. Seong's vehicle was involved.

06:23.049 --> 06:24.133
So?

06:24.134 --> 06:25.968
"His Majesty was in that car

06:25.969 --> 06:28.304
and the Grand Prince caused
an accident to save him,

06:28.305 --> 06:31.725
racking up countless traffic violations
and substantial damage in the process."

06:32.350 --> 06:34.018
If word of this got out,

06:34.019 --> 06:35.020
all of this could be blamed

06:36.146 --> 06:37.230
on the young king.

06:39.065 --> 06:40.149
Prime Minister Min.

06:40.150 --> 06:42.402
I am merely stating that it could lead

06:43.153 --> 06:44.279
to such dire conclusions.

06:46.865 --> 06:48.533
Are you trying to protect that maiden?

06:50.160 --> 06:52.329
I am trying to protect the Crown.

07:00.503 --> 07:02.380
OPERATING CENTER

07:03.798 --> 07:05.050
LEE ♪
IN RECOVERY

07:11.723 --> 07:13.058
The surgery went well.

07:13.558 --> 07:15.267
The anesthesia has just worn off,

07:15.268 --> 07:18.355
so he should be able to go up
to his room in about an hour.

07:20.190 --> 07:22.399
What about any lasting effects?

07:22.400 --> 07:26.570
I heard it can be difficult
to use your arm after shoulder surgery.

07:26.571 --> 07:29.239
The surgery wasn't due to a fracture
or a chronic condition,

07:29.240 --> 07:30.367
so that is unlikely.

07:31.034 --> 07:32.451
- No need to worry.
- Thank you.

07:32.452 --> 07:34.287
- Thank you, Doctor.
- Thank you.

07:35.705 --> 07:36.997
Thank goodness.

07:36.998 --> 07:38.291
- That's a relief.
- Yes.

08:03.566 --> 08:06.235
Let's increase security
on the floor Ms. Seong is on.

08:06.236 --> 08:08.070
- Send people from our office.
- Yes, sir.

08:08.071 --> 08:10.030
Let me know as soon as she wakes up.

08:10.031 --> 08:11.241
Yes, sir.
:cue

08:24.504 --> 08:26.047
SEONG HUIJU

09:04.002 --> 09:06.087
Ms. Seong.

09:08.715 --> 09:09.799
Your Majesty?

09:10.467 --> 09:12.260
Are you awake?

09:15.472 --> 09:17.474
Your Majesty! Are you all right?

09:18.516 --> 09:19.850
Is anything broken?

09:21.519 --> 09:22.645
I am sorry.

09:24.314 --> 09:27.192
This all happened
because I insisted on a drive.

09:30.737 --> 09:31.738
Not at all.

09:32.947 --> 09:34.991
Your Majesty and I are both fine.

09:39.079 --> 09:40.455
Wait, His Royal Highness.

09:41.164 --> 09:43.248
Where is the Grand Prince?
Is he here as well?

09:43.249 --> 09:44.917
Do not worry.

09:44.918 --> 09:47.544
Uncle did not faint.

09:47.545 --> 09:50.006
He even went into the operating room
without crying.

09:50.507 --> 09:52.633
The operating room?

09:52.634 --> 09:55.011
He's having surgery?

09:55.762 --> 09:58.264
Would you like some water?

09:59.015 --> 10:00.599
Is the surgery over?

10:00.600 --> 10:01.601
Are you okay?

10:03.937 --> 10:06.188
I mean, what were you thinking,
jumping in there?

10:06.189 --> 10:07.273
Are you insane?

10:07.774 --> 10:10.984
Ms. Seong, His Royal Highness
has just woken up from the anesthesia…

10:10.985 --> 10:12.612
- You can't just--
- Hold on.

10:13.404 --> 10:15.656
You even hurt your face?

10:15.657 --> 10:17.826
When that's all you have going for you?

10:24.874 --> 10:25.875
Oh, no.

10:27.252 --> 10:28.253
How are you doing?

10:32.507 --> 10:33.508
You were unconscious.

10:36.594 --> 10:37.637
I'm perfectly fine.

10:49.816 --> 10:50.817
Come here.

10:56.030 --> 10:57.157
I'm hurting.

11:26.311 --> 11:27.437
Anywhere else?

11:29.939 --> 11:30.940
I'm fine.

11:46.873 --> 11:48.791
Don't ever jump in like that again.

11:52.086 --> 11:54.672
I need to you stay in one piece
so you can have my back.

11:55.882 --> 11:57.841
You were lucky this time.

11:57.842 --> 12:00.469
Imagine if your life
was in danger…

12:00.470 --> 12:02.931
You think it would end
with just a few eggs?

12:03.473 --> 12:05.433
Then stop putting me in that position.
:cue

12:08.519 --> 12:09.812
I can't promise you that.

12:11.189 --> 12:12.357
Then I can't either.

12:15.109 --> 12:18.029
You make it seem like
you're madly in love with me.

12:21.074 --> 12:22.951
This is what should be
making the headlines.

12:36.047 --> 12:37.714
Babe, you sure this is right?

12:37.715 --> 12:39.424
Yeah, you're almost there.

12:39.425 --> 12:40.592
Okay.

12:40.593 --> 12:43.679
Now put one hand on your chest. Namaste.

12:43.680 --> 12:45.055
What? Nama-what-now?

12:45.056 --> 12:46.556
Namaste.

12:46.557 --> 12:48.850
Right. Nama…

12:48.851 --> 12:50.436
FATHER

12:51.271 --> 12:52.980
- Babe, Father's calling.
- What?

12:52.981 --> 12:54.606
Now? Why?

12:54.607 --> 12:56.484
- Does he know you're not at work?
- Darn it.

12:59.404 --> 13:00.530
It's not even 8:00 yet.

13:01.030 --> 13:02.864
That's true. Did you do something wrong?

13:02.865 --> 13:03.866
No, I didn't.

13:04.409 --> 13:05.410
Hello, Father.

13:06.327 --> 13:08.454
What? Seong Huiju did?

13:09.122 --> 13:11.207
What in the… Babe, turn the TV on.

13:13.376 --> 13:14.377
Yes.

13:15.169 --> 13:19.256
Last night, a traffic accident occurred
on an outlying road in Gyeonggi Province.

13:19.257 --> 13:21.258
- A speeding sports car
- Yes, just a moment.

13:21.259 --> 13:23.677
collided with a vehicle
in the adjacent lane.

13:23.678 --> 13:26.430
The driver of the sports car
was identified as CEO Seong Huiju

13:26.431 --> 13:28.974
of Castle Beauty,
sparking further controversy.

13:28.975 --> 13:31.184
It is being reported
that Ms. Seong's vehicle

13:31.185 --> 13:33.145
was traveling 50 km/h
over the speed limit…

13:33.146 --> 13:35.480
- What do we do?
- Father, we'll come to you now.

13:35.481 --> 13:38.234
- The police are still investigating…
- All right.

13:38.901 --> 13:39.944
You can't come in here.

13:40.653 --> 13:43.071
Seriously? Don't you remember me
from last time?

13:43.072 --> 13:44.823
I'm her assistant at Castle Beauty.

13:44.824 --> 13:46.450
You can't. Please step back.

13:46.451 --> 13:48.244
This is driving me insane.

13:49.287 --> 13:50.329
Then what about him?

13:53.041 --> 13:56.044
Come on! Why do you only ever stop me?

13:56.878 --> 13:58.170
Ms. Seong!

13:58.171 --> 13:59.881
Ms. Do, come here.

14:01.507 --> 14:02.675
She's with me.

14:03.885 --> 14:05.678
Those jerks are the worst.

14:07.138 --> 14:08.139
Unbelievable.

14:09.348 --> 14:10.391
Why do they keep…

14:12.852 --> 14:15.354
I told you I'm fine.

14:15.897 --> 14:17.272
Nothing to worry about.

14:17.273 --> 14:19.233
I'm totally fine.

14:19.984 --> 14:21.194
You'll fix this, right?

14:25.239 --> 14:26.782
LIVE 3-MIN CHART

14:26.783 --> 14:28.950
This was all part of the plan, right?

14:28.951 --> 14:32.246
The chairman is freaking out.
He wants you as soon as you're discharged.

14:34.415 --> 14:35.582
He knows I was injured?

14:35.583 --> 14:36.834
Of course…

14:40.755 --> 14:42.297
he does.

14:42.298 --> 14:44.092
And still, not a single word?

14:44.926 --> 14:46.803
Not from Father, or even Seong Taeju?

14:49.305 --> 14:51.807
I mean, how did you even end up
in that accident?

14:54.018 --> 14:55.977
- Did you drink and drive?
- No, I didn't.

14:55.978 --> 14:57.021
I swear I didn't.

14:58.147 --> 15:01.483
Then were you just speeding
for the thrill of it?

15:02.860 --> 15:04.486
You think I'm some kind of lunatic?

15:04.487 --> 15:06.697
Just randomly speeding
for the thrill of it?

15:08.407 --> 15:09.951
The car just took off.

15:10.868 --> 15:12.662
The brakes and all weren't working.

15:14.080 --> 15:15.081
What in the world…

15:16.666 --> 15:20.253
Then I'll first prepare a press release
with the dashcam footage.

15:20.837 --> 15:22.879
- You can't.
- Why not?

15:22.880 --> 15:24.715
You just can't.

15:28.261 --> 15:29.846
His Majesty was with me.

15:30.513 --> 15:31.514
His Majesty?

15:32.515 --> 15:33.933
As in His Majesty the King?

15:35.643 --> 15:37.520
The investigation won't be public.

15:43.484 --> 15:44.568
Damn it.

15:44.569 --> 15:45.903
It just never ends!

15:50.241 --> 15:51.450
Let's reconsider this.

15:52.451 --> 15:54.452
- Reconsider what?
- This marriage.

15:54.453 --> 15:55.663
Can't you just call it off?

15:56.372 --> 15:59.457
You're seriously bringing that up now?
:cue

15:59.458 --> 16:02.752
There has been nothing but trouble
since Prince I-AN entered your life.

16:02.753 --> 16:05.046
Egged at your own door
over a little scandal.

16:05.047 --> 16:07.716
One wrong turn in the palace
made you an arsonist.

16:07.717 --> 16:10.302
And this time, you nearly died.

16:10.303 --> 16:12.596
Grand Prince I-AN was the one
who saved me.

16:12.597 --> 16:14.307
Wait, he was the one who saved you?

16:15.266 --> 16:17.310
Why are you two so caught up in this?

16:18.019 --> 16:19.311
What do you mean?

16:19.312 --> 16:21.938
I mean, why are you two overdoing it?

16:21.939 --> 16:23.815
You'll be divorced in three years anyway.

16:23.816 --> 16:25.025
"Divorced"?

16:27.737 --> 16:28.738
Jeongwoo.

16:48.216 --> 16:49.508
Where did you pop out from?

16:50.134 --> 16:51.677
Is your job fun?

16:52.511 --> 16:53.803
Pardon?

16:53.804 --> 16:55.139
Working at the palace.

16:55.765 --> 16:56.849
Oh, the palace?

16:57.683 --> 16:58.684
Well…

16:59.185 --> 17:01.604
Why? Are you looking to work there too?

17:02.730 --> 17:03.731
Wow.

17:05.942 --> 17:07.568
When Ms. Seong moves into the palace…

17:12.198 --> 17:13.407
I'll be following her.

17:21.457 --> 17:22.625
So charismatic.

17:34.387 --> 17:35.638
You said it was genuine.

17:36.264 --> 17:37.681
Was it all a lie?

17:37.682 --> 17:40.475
I wouldn't go so far as to call it a lie…

17:40.476 --> 17:42.227
Seong Huiju.

17:42.228 --> 17:43.813
It's like a marriage of convenience.

17:44.355 --> 17:45.856
A simple exchange of services.

17:46.482 --> 17:48.400
You know plenty of people like that.

17:48.401 --> 17:49.943
Don't make a big deal out of it.

17:49.944 --> 17:51.237
That's completely different.

17:51.821 --> 17:52.862
How so?

17:52.863 --> 17:55.241
Don't you know how dangerous
the palace can be?

17:55.866 --> 17:57.785
- Even this accident--
- I'm fine.

17:59.203 --> 18:01.205
You think I proposed without knowing that?

18:01.914 --> 18:02.999
You proposed to him?

18:04.250 --> 18:06.877
Yeah. I was rejected about three times.

18:14.719 --> 18:15.720
Listen.

18:16.304 --> 18:18.097
I have everything but status.

18:18.598 --> 18:20.599
I have the money, talent, and ambition,

18:20.600 --> 18:22.393
but status is the one thing I don't have.

18:22.893 --> 18:24.186
If I just had that…

18:25.938 --> 18:27.897
I mean, why can't I have that too?

18:27.898 --> 18:28.982
Is that all?

18:33.154 --> 18:34.989
The reason you want to marry him.

18:35.865 --> 18:37.283
Is status all there is to it?

18:38.909 --> 18:40.411
What else could there be?

18:53.674 --> 18:54.675
Then do it with me.

18:56.010 --> 18:57.219
Do what?

18:58.763 --> 19:00.848
Just marry me instead.

19:04.143 --> 19:05.311
That will not do.

19:06.854 --> 19:09.523
The Grand Prince, who had surgery,
is returning to the palace.

19:10.650 --> 19:12.359
Then surely, the King should as well.

19:12.360 --> 19:14.110
But, Your Majesty…

19:14.111 --> 19:15.945
If the king remains out of sight,

19:15.946 --> 19:18.616
the people will come to think
they do not need one.

19:21.452 --> 19:22.662
Do you not agree?

19:24.789 --> 19:26.290
I agree.

19:32.421 --> 19:35.090
Your Royal Highness, I've been discharged…

19:35.091 --> 19:36.092
Huh?

19:40.221 --> 19:41.972
Has he already been discharged?
:cue

19:48.062 --> 19:50.773
Your Royal Highness,
Prime Minister Min has arrived.

19:53.693 --> 19:54.777
Show him in.

19:58.823 --> 19:59.824
Your Royal Highness.

20:01.701 --> 20:02.743
You are all dismissed.

20:26.976 --> 20:28.060
I mean,

20:28.602 --> 20:32.815
he should at least tell me
if he's been discharged.

20:33.691 --> 20:36.110
Not a great sign for married life.

20:37.570 --> 20:39.488
He didn't say anything at the hospital?

20:39.989 --> 20:40.990
When?

20:41.532 --> 20:43.951
The last time I saw him
was early this morning.

20:44.493 --> 20:45.494
What?

20:57.423 --> 20:59.466
But he was standing
outside your room earlier.

20:59.467 --> 21:02.135
My room? When?

21:02.136 --> 21:04.054
When Prime Minister Min stopped by.

21:05.222 --> 21:06.639
Then do it with me.

21:06.640 --> 21:09.017
Just marry me instead.

21:17.109 --> 21:19.862
Huh?

21:21.572 --> 21:23.281
So what you're saying is

21:23.282 --> 21:26.534
Ms. Seong was kicked out
by His Royal Highness?

21:26.535 --> 21:29.497
Well, I mean, it was more like…

21:30.289 --> 21:31.748
He asked that you return home.

21:31.749 --> 21:33.875
That's the same thing!

21:38.547 --> 21:39.714
PRINCE

21:39.715 --> 21:41.341
Is he kidding me right now?

21:49.183 --> 21:51.644
Your Ladyship! Wait, Your Ladyship.

21:53.604 --> 21:54.605
It's fine.

21:55.356 --> 21:57.233
The master of the house
has already spoken.

21:58.234 --> 21:59.527
It's not that.

22:02.154 --> 22:03.155
The hopae.

22:04.365 --> 22:05.533
He would like it returned.

22:53.247 --> 22:56.417
JUNIOR ALUM

23:08.429 --> 23:09.430
Is that all?

23:11.307 --> 23:13.350
The reason you want to marry him.

23:13.976 --> 23:15.269
Is status all there is to it?

23:15.811 --> 23:16.979
What else could there be?

23:17.730 --> 23:18.981
Then do it with me.

23:20.357 --> 23:22.484
Just marry me instead.
:cue

23:41.879 --> 23:43.255
Say it to my face.

23:44.173 --> 23:45.174
Whatever it is.

24:20.709 --> 24:24.421
It is a relief that
I will never have to teach you.

24:28.801 --> 24:30.970
No matter how great a teacher may be,

24:31.470 --> 24:34.974
there are things
that simply cannot be taught.

24:39.353 --> 24:40.521
Pardon?

24:51.824 --> 24:55.244
Your Royal Highness,
Ms. Seong Huiju has arrived.

24:57.079 --> 24:58.622
Are you cleared to be out already?

25:01.917 --> 25:02.918
That's your concern?

25:08.632 --> 25:10.217
Why did you kick me out?

25:11.260 --> 25:12.553
Because of the Queen Mother?

25:16.890 --> 25:17.891
Or…

25:18.976 --> 25:20.102
because of Jeongwoo?

25:21.729 --> 25:22.730
What about him?

25:25.232 --> 25:26.983
Didn't you overhear something?

25:26.984 --> 25:28.068
What?

25:29.236 --> 25:30.237
Never mind.

25:31.947 --> 25:34.157
Then why did you kick me out?

25:34.158 --> 25:36.869
I need to know what's going on
before I play along or not.

25:39.621 --> 25:41.206
Someone messed with your car.

25:42.541 --> 25:44.001
That is what caused the accident.

25:47.880 --> 25:49.006
Who?

25:49.673 --> 25:50.716
It's being investigated.

25:51.759 --> 25:52.885
We will catch them.

25:55.345 --> 25:56.346
And so,

25:57.890 --> 25:59.348
I'm changing the plan.

26:02.770 --> 26:03.771
Let's…

26:08.025 --> 26:09.068
call off this marriage.

26:14.782 --> 26:16.992
What… What was that?

26:19.411 --> 26:21.497
Call what off now?

26:23.332 --> 26:24.333
The marriage.

26:26.919 --> 26:28.128
But why?

26:28.879 --> 26:30.588
Did Queen Mother tell you to do that?

26:30.589 --> 26:32.256
Because of the accident?

26:32.257 --> 26:34.384
That was because
His Majesty was relentless.

26:35.010 --> 26:37.386
And you said someone messed with my car.

26:37.387 --> 26:39.430
That makes me a victim too.

26:39.431 --> 26:40.432
Exactly.

26:42.184 --> 26:43.560
That's why we must call it off.

26:47.064 --> 26:49.024
If I married someone like you

26:49.900 --> 26:52.152
who breaks every rule
and has enemies at every turn…

26:54.655 --> 26:56.532
the Crown is bound to fall.

27:15.384 --> 27:19.011
Father, this is a serious accident.
:cue

27:19.012 --> 27:20.429
See here.

27:20.430 --> 27:23.224
God, she's even driving
on the other side of the road.

27:23.225 --> 27:25.518
If you ask me, at best, she's drunk.

27:25.519 --> 27:27.980
At worst, it's hard drugs.
Nowadays, there's this…

27:29.523 --> 27:30.606
Right.

27:30.607 --> 27:33.651
I mean, she's always been
desperate for attention.

27:33.652 --> 27:37.280
Now that she's dating Prince I-AN,
she's become a total hot tomato.

27:37.281 --> 27:38.323
- And…
- Potato.

27:39.491 --> 27:41.868
It's "hot potato."
Like a freshly baked hot potato.

27:41.869 --> 27:43.287
Oh, right. Potato.

27:43.787 --> 27:44.913
So, now…

27:45.497 --> 27:46.956
Babe, does that matter?

27:46.957 --> 27:48.750
Tomato. Potato. Same difference.

27:49.293 --> 27:50.377
Sometimes, you can be…

27:51.086 --> 27:56.132
Anyway, Father, this is totally
a huge, glaring owner-related risk.

27:56.133 --> 27:58.634
You saw how the stock
had shot up over the last few days

27:58.635 --> 28:00.428
and just took a nosedive, didn't you?

28:00.429 --> 28:02.639
At this rate, Castle Beauty will just…

28:04.057 --> 28:05.309
So what?

28:08.228 --> 28:09.854
You want to take over Beauty?

28:09.855 --> 28:11.899
Is that any way to speak to your brother?

28:12.524 --> 28:14.275
What is it?

28:14.276 --> 28:16.111
Let's make this quick. I'm busy.

28:18.530 --> 28:19.865
Explain yourself.

28:22.075 --> 28:23.869
What is there to explain?

28:24.828 --> 28:26.203
It's just as you see.

28:26.204 --> 28:27.789
Can you handle the consequences?

28:28.290 --> 28:29.958
We'll issue a press release soon.

28:31.335 --> 28:32.336
Neither alcohol

28:33.253 --> 28:34.837
nor drugs were involved.

28:34.838 --> 28:36.798
I heard they moved all your things

28:37.591 --> 28:39.092
out of his house today.

28:39.760 --> 28:41.677
Did you have me followed?

28:41.678 --> 28:43.346
Explain yourself first!

28:46.975 --> 28:48.769
It's just a lovers' spat.

28:50.062 --> 28:51.145
Satisfied?

28:51.146 --> 28:52.730
You call yourself a businesswoman,

28:52.731 --> 28:54.899
yet you don't even realize
you're being used.

28:54.900 --> 28:57.277
The Grand Prince has used you
for all you're worth.

28:58.695 --> 29:02.240
He acted like he was above status,
as if he had no ambition for the throne.

29:03.033 --> 29:04.993
Now that he has everything…

29:07.996 --> 29:09.497
he's tossing you out.

29:12.376 --> 29:13.377
So what?

29:15.170 --> 29:16.463
What's the issue?

29:18.423 --> 29:20.008
Two can play that game.

29:21.551 --> 29:24.221
Do you know how much our stock
has jumped at the news

29:25.013 --> 29:27.515
of Castle Group's Seong Huiju
marrying into the royal family?

29:27.516 --> 29:30.309
Hey, kid. It all tanked today.

29:30.310 --> 29:32.729
It will bounce right back
after the press release, damn it.

29:36.984 --> 29:39.987
They're even asking if the "Castle" name
was part of some grand plan.

29:40.654 --> 29:41.737
Haven't you seen the news?

29:41.738 --> 29:44.615
Did it ever cross your mind that
it'll put a bigger target on our backs?

29:44.616 --> 29:46.201
So we take a few hits!

29:48.078 --> 29:49.662
A few hits won't kill you.

29:53.417 --> 29:55.293
And even if it did, what of it?

29:56.795 --> 29:58.255
We all end up dead anyway.

29:59.047 --> 30:01.091
What, do you plan to live forever?

30:02.384 --> 30:04.428
Next time, just text me instead.

30:05.679 --> 30:08.682
If you want to yell that badly,
then feel free to call.

30:12.144 --> 30:14.103
- Sit down.
- I have plans.

30:14.104 --> 30:15.105
Seong Huiju!

30:19.109 --> 30:20.110
It's me.

30:20.652 --> 30:22.529
I need you to look into something for me.

30:33.790 --> 30:35.417
Find out who last worked
on my car.

30:37.669 --> 30:41.298
Dig up everything
you possibly can on them.
:cue

30:47.387 --> 30:49.139
A grand prince of this nation can't…

30:50.766 --> 30:52.726
break an engagement.

30:53.268 --> 30:56.604
Technically, there's nothing to break.
We were never engaged.

30:56.605 --> 30:57.688
Are you kidding?

30:57.689 --> 31:00.733
After all that talk
about getting married and living together?

31:00.734 --> 31:01.984
We never lived together.

31:01.985 --> 31:04.071
- I was at the palace, and she was--
- Listen.

31:06.156 --> 31:09.533
Even if you killed someone,
I would take your side.

31:09.534 --> 31:10.869
But this is not cool. It's--

31:12.037 --> 31:13.914
Why would you side with a murderer?

31:15.332 --> 31:17.209
You must've had your reasons.

31:18.126 --> 31:20.211
So, why did you break it off?

31:20.212 --> 31:22.297
- I didn't "break"--
- Seriously? Come on.

31:23.090 --> 31:24.299
That's not what I'm asking.

31:27.135 --> 31:29.012
Why did you break it off?

31:39.356 --> 31:40.357
To keep her alive.

31:43.568 --> 31:46.821
Mother, should we pick up
fried chicken on the way to the palace?

31:46.822 --> 31:47.905
Fried chicken?

31:47.906 --> 31:50.200
Hwan texted and said he wanted some.

31:51.701 --> 31:53.786
He's always making me do stuff like this.

31:53.787 --> 31:56.248
Shall we, then?

31:56.873 --> 31:57.874
Yes, Mother.

32:24.317 --> 32:25.735
Mother!

32:55.390 --> 32:58.268
Mother, should we pick up
fried chicken on the way to the palace?

33:00.145 --> 33:01.396
Shall we, then?

33:08.904 --> 33:10.447
Mother…

33:11.615 --> 33:12.824
Mother…

33:48.485 --> 33:50.111
There wasn't a doubt in my mind.

33:50.779 --> 33:53.657
It was a moment
I'd regretted countless times.

34:09.297 --> 34:10.590
That's what changed my mind.

34:13.009 --> 34:14.261
It was just an accident.

34:15.178 --> 34:17.347
It wasn't even your fault, so why?

34:20.058 --> 34:21.101
It was my fault.

34:23.228 --> 34:24.521
Signs of deliberate tampering

34:25.105 --> 34:26.815
were found in the accident vehicle.

34:28.233 --> 34:31.736
We'll need to investigate further
to determine if they were targeting

34:32.279 --> 34:33.738
His Majesty or Ms. Seong.

34:38.076 --> 34:40.704
However, do not concern yourself too much.
:cue

34:42.664 --> 34:44.581
I will do everything
in my power to protect

34:44.582 --> 34:46.042
His Majesty, Your Royal Highness,

34:47.335 --> 34:48.503
and the Crown.

34:52.132 --> 34:53.133
In turn,

34:53.758 --> 34:54.843
I'd like to ask you

34:56.720 --> 34:59.139
to protect Ms. Seong Huiju.

35:01.433 --> 35:03.518
Please cast her far away from the palace.

35:05.312 --> 35:08.064
I sincerely implore you,
Your Royal Highness.

35:13.820 --> 35:14.946
That is why

35:16.197 --> 35:17.324
I must step aside.

35:19.409 --> 35:20.410
Your Royal Highness.

35:20.952 --> 35:22.037
Thus,

35:23.580 --> 35:24.623
I want to do something.

35:25.832 --> 35:26.833
Pardon?

35:28.501 --> 35:29.502
A parting gift.

35:31.296 --> 35:32.297
For her.

35:43.725 --> 35:45.392
The Inner Court Banquet guest list,

35:45.393 --> 35:47.061
proposed by the Royal Secretariat.

35:47.062 --> 35:49.438
PALACE EVENT HOSTED
FOR LADIES OF THE INNER COURT

35:49.439 --> 35:51.316
TRADITIONALLY HELD
SINCE THE JOSEON DYNASTY

35:53.360 --> 35:55.695
Remove the scandal-ridden figures.

35:59.491 --> 36:00.700
No new money either.

36:03.119 --> 36:05.329
The merits of these two are comparable.

36:05.330 --> 36:07.331
Bring me the details of their families.

36:07.332 --> 36:08.666
Yes, Your Majesty.

36:08.667 --> 36:10.585
Your standards rise every year.

36:11.461 --> 36:14.880
The more exclusive the guest list,

36:14.881 --> 36:17.759
the deeper the despair of the uninvited.

36:18.802 --> 36:22.347
And with it comes
the greater delight of those invited.

36:23.390 --> 36:24.808
INNER COURT BANQUET GUEST LIST

36:27.727 --> 36:30.062
Another gathering
of the usual suspects this year.

36:30.063 --> 36:31.230
All nobility.

36:31.231 --> 36:32.816
The competition is fiercer every year.

36:33.441 --> 36:35.234
It does offer many benefits.

36:35.235 --> 36:36.694
That is true.

36:36.695 --> 36:38.696
But if they managed to secure an invite,

36:38.697 --> 36:41.532
they must already possess
plenty of money and land.

36:43.785 --> 36:46.579
That's precisely why they're willing
to die for royal prestige.

36:47.247 --> 36:49.290
It's the only thing their money can't buy.

36:54.170 --> 36:55.462
Ma'am.

36:55.463 --> 36:58.257
I had to jump through
some pretty high hoops to secure

36:58.258 --> 37:00.509
this Inner Court Banquet guest list.

37:00.510 --> 37:02.177
A lot of familiar faces, right?

37:02.178 --> 37:04.680
A gathering of female business leaders
in their thirties…

37:04.681 --> 37:06.598
Still just 20 of them, right?

37:06.599 --> 37:09.101
Not even enough for a soccer match.

37:09.102 --> 37:10.728
But, ma'am, you said so yourself.

37:10.729 --> 37:13.230
"One absolute is worth
more than a hundred maybes."

37:13.231 --> 37:14.857
These are 20 absolutes.

37:14.858 --> 37:16.609
All backed by the Crown, no less!

37:20.697 --> 37:23.532
You once called this
the most luxurious marketing strategy…

37:23.533 --> 37:25.576
So what's your point?

37:25.577 --> 37:27.119
Moving on.

37:27.120 --> 37:30.122
Since you have ties
with the palace and all, we thought

37:30.123 --> 37:32.791
one of the guests could be
a new face of our luxury line.

37:32.792 --> 37:33.752
Yes, so we…

37:34.252 --> 37:35.837
Just a moment. Oh.

37:40.550 --> 37:41.843
Hello.

37:42.594 --> 37:43.595
Hello.

37:44.804 --> 37:47.890
MS. SEONG HUIJU, YOU ARE CORDIALLY INVITED
TO THE INNER COURT BANQUET

37:49.184 --> 37:50.642
Me?

37:50.643 --> 37:51.978
Yes, Ms. Seong.

37:53.688 --> 37:58.192
The Inner Court Banquet
is a very important annual event.

37:58.193 --> 38:00.737
Of course, I'm aware
of the Inner Court Banquet.

38:01.696 --> 38:05.908
But I thought only noblewomen
were invited to this.

38:05.909 --> 38:08.535
What? No such criterion exists…

38:08.536 --> 38:09.912
It certainly doesn't,

38:09.913 --> 38:11.289
but that's how it's been done.

38:12.123 --> 38:14.334
For 600 years, without a single exception.

38:18.505 --> 38:21.882
The thing about change is that
it happens gradually…

38:21.883 --> 38:23.050
So? How? Why?

38:23.051 --> 38:26.262
Why have I suddenly been invited?

38:26.763 --> 38:30.349
Yes, well, you've experienced
some hardships recently,

38:30.350 --> 38:33.853
and the press release
about your breakup is about to go out.

38:34.354 --> 38:37.689
So to make it clear the palace
wasn't responsible for your breakup…

38:37.690 --> 38:40.526
You want to stage a performance
for the public?
:cue

38:49.702 --> 38:51.161
Yes, you see,

38:51.162 --> 38:53.455
the dress codes
for the two parts are different.

38:53.456 --> 38:55.707
It's customary to wear
a dangui for the reception.

38:55.708 --> 38:59.169
The Queen Mother will wear white,
so it's best to avoid that color.

38:59.170 --> 39:00.838
No thanks.

39:00.839 --> 39:03.216
To what exactly? The dangui?

39:04.425 --> 39:06.177
The Inner Court Banquet.

39:09.097 --> 39:10.305
Ms. Seong.

39:10.306 --> 39:11.557
Why?

39:11.558 --> 39:13.685
The Inner Court Banquet?
You don't want to attend?

39:15.603 --> 39:18.438
Silly me, how did I forget
to mention this?

39:18.439 --> 39:22.818
Attending it once will lead
to many more royal invitations.

39:22.819 --> 39:25.487
Even royal patronage
for your overseas business.

39:25.488 --> 39:27.073
Okay. Above all else,

39:27.574 --> 39:31.118
this will confirm that you two
didn't end things badly,

39:31.119 --> 39:33.912
and that you remain
on good terms with the Crown.

39:33.913 --> 39:36.164
We can pivot
to an "it's all cool" narrative--

39:36.165 --> 39:37.791
- That would be excellent.
- Mm-hmm.

39:37.792 --> 39:39.334
You've always wanted an invite.

39:39.335 --> 39:42.130
That was before marriage was on the table.

39:43.548 --> 39:44.882
No thanks.

39:44.883 --> 39:47.801
But still, His Royal Highness personally…

39:47.802 --> 39:48.970
No…

39:49.762 --> 39:51.055
thank…

39:53.224 --> 39:54.225
you.

39:56.185 --> 39:57.352
What?

39:57.353 --> 39:59.354
So? You just left?

39:59.355 --> 40:03.443
What choice did I have? She was about
to murder me in broad daylight.

40:08.197 --> 40:10.783
I heard you moved Seong Huiju
out of your private residence.

40:12.952 --> 40:14.329
What are you playing at?

40:15.872 --> 40:17.123
I am protecting her.

40:18.499 --> 40:19.792
Her ties to the Crown

40:20.835 --> 40:22.377
have only led her to misfortune.

40:22.378 --> 40:23.588
Then,

40:24.672 --> 40:26.758
ensure she no longer has any ties
to the Crown.

40:27.759 --> 40:28.843
That is my intention.

40:32.931 --> 40:33.973
I will not pursue

40:35.475 --> 40:36.684
marriage with Seong Huiju.

40:37.810 --> 40:38.811
In turn,

40:39.312 --> 40:41.439
I ask that you invite her
to the Inner Court Banquet.

40:42.649 --> 40:44.025
I do not wish to see her suffer

40:44.776 --> 40:46.235
because of our parting.

40:51.991 --> 40:53.117
Summon her to the palace.

40:54.035 --> 40:55.286
Ms. Seong Huiju?

40:55.787 --> 40:56.788
You want me to?

40:58.373 --> 41:01.376
I shall persuade her myself.

41:02.502 --> 41:03.544
No thanks.

41:05.296 --> 41:06.589
No, thank you.

41:07.966 --> 41:09.467
Who is he to summon me?

41:13.137 --> 41:14.889
Is the fried chicken here?

41:15.640 --> 41:18.184
What? You ordered fried chicken again?

41:21.646 --> 41:23.022
You open it.

41:31.614 --> 41:32.740
Mmm.

41:33.324 --> 41:35.742
People have nothing
on fried chicken, right?

41:35.743 --> 41:37.828
It shows up right on time
when you call them.

41:37.829 --> 41:39.455
You never get sick of it.

41:39.998 --> 41:41.207
Always so reliable.

41:42.667 --> 41:43.876
- Wait…
- What?

41:44.502 --> 41:46.254
Are you upset you got dumped?

41:48.506 --> 41:50.883
Why would you say that
when I'm enjoying fried chicken?

41:51.426 --> 41:52.427
I'm done.

41:54.512 --> 41:56.514
Oh, I mean…

41:58.057 --> 42:00.810
Why are you so upset?

42:01.310 --> 42:03.104
It was all pretend.

42:04.272 --> 42:06.649
That's exactly why.

42:08.192 --> 42:10.402
Relationships end
when one side loses interest,

42:10.403 --> 42:11.945
whether the other likes it or not.

42:11.946 --> 42:13.572
But that's not what this was.

42:13.573 --> 42:15.408
This was strictly a contract.

42:17.410 --> 42:18.786
Father was right.

42:19.620 --> 42:23.124
I'm a businesswoman. I should've known
better than to trust a stranger.

42:24.042 --> 42:25.710
I should've drawn up a contract.
:cue

42:37.597 --> 42:38.722
Ms. Seong, the invite--

42:38.723 --> 42:39.974
No thanks.

42:40.558 --> 42:41.559
Ms. Seong.

42:42.101 --> 42:43.185
No thanks.

42:43.186 --> 42:46.189
-  You're really not going?
- No, thank you!

42:51.402 --> 42:52.569
Is she dumb?

42:52.570 --> 42:54.738
Just give up already.

42:54.739 --> 42:56.656
She doesn't want anything to do with you.

42:56.657 --> 42:57.950
Choi Hyeon.

43:00.745 --> 43:02.205
I mean, I can't blame her.

43:02.705 --> 43:05.041
You dumped her
and now you're acting so uncool.

43:11.756 --> 43:13.131
Hey, Ms. Seong.

43:13.132 --> 43:15.300
I went to the repair shop and secured

43:15.301 --> 43:18.054
the résumé of the bastard
who tampered with your car and fled.

43:18.763 --> 43:21.181
They ran a search with his photo,

43:21.182 --> 43:23.684
but he doesn't seem to have any priors.

43:24.477 --> 43:28.231
He must've bought
something there at least once.

43:28.815 --> 43:29.816
What?

43:30.441 --> 43:32.568
There's a convenience store
in front of the shop.

43:33.444 --> 43:34.903
Oh, right.

43:34.904 --> 43:37.239
Scour their CCTV footage.

43:37.240 --> 43:38.991
I want his purchase history.

43:47.333 --> 43:48.417
Say it to my face.

43:49.418 --> 43:50.419
Whatever it is.

44:09.647 --> 44:11.232
Are you afraid to go to the banquet?

44:14.360 --> 44:16.445
I will prepare everything you need.

44:17.738 --> 44:18.823
From the clothes

44:19.490 --> 44:20.907
to the etiquette lessons.

44:20.908 --> 44:22.201
Why?

44:23.035 --> 44:26.956
I break every rule
and have enemies at every turn.

44:27.957 --> 44:29.749
- So why would I go there?
- Seong Huiju.

44:29.750 --> 44:31.794
Then provide me with a convincing reason.

44:33.171 --> 44:36.089
You risked your life to save me,
just to break off the engagement.

44:36.090 --> 44:38.593
And now you're inviting me
to the Inner Court Banquet?

44:39.552 --> 44:40.802
A split personality?

44:40.803 --> 44:42.221
I am trying to protect you!

44:44.223 --> 44:45.391
We're not even married…

44:47.977 --> 44:49.729
and you've been attacked multiple times.

44:51.272 --> 44:52.815
And once the breakup news breaks,

44:54.734 --> 44:56.152
it'll only get worse.

44:57.028 --> 44:58.029
So what?

44:59.363 --> 45:02.575
"Social ascent is dangerous.
Be content with an invite to the banquet."

45:03.492 --> 45:05.745
- Is that it?
- Just stay out of harm's way.

45:07.413 --> 45:08.581
Is that so difficult?

45:11.918 --> 45:12.919
Coward.

45:15.129 --> 45:16.338
What?

45:29.435 --> 45:31.312
- What are you…
- You like cats.

45:33.147 --> 45:34.148
Try protecting them.

45:35.149 --> 45:36.442
I'm going to attack them.

45:45.701 --> 45:47.245
What the hell are you doing?

45:56.712 --> 45:58.422
This is how you protect someone.

45:59.882 --> 46:00.967
You go on the offensive.

46:01.926 --> 46:03.219
You fight back.

46:15.523 --> 46:17.440
You never learned to bend.

46:17.441 --> 46:20.653
You only know how to bend.
That's why you lose to people beneath you.

46:22.238 --> 46:23.781
I asked you for status,

46:24.740 --> 46:27.034
not a cozy cradle to hide from the world.

46:31.330 --> 46:32.540
Do not bend to their will.
:cue

46:33.874 --> 46:35.167
Do not back away

46:36.794 --> 46:38.129
and do not compromise.

46:41.549 --> 46:43.175
That's how you and I both

46:44.719 --> 46:46.053
get what we want.

46:57.773 --> 46:59.150
She is one scary lady.

47:00.609 --> 47:03.236
I know all's fair in love and war,

47:03.237 --> 47:04.863
but isn't this taking it too far?

47:04.864 --> 47:06.740
Is a "safe exit" an option here?

47:06.741 --> 47:08.658
I told you I hurt myself.

47:08.659 --> 47:11.870
Even so, how could she let
your precious body be injured?

47:11.871 --> 47:13.538
She has crossed the line.

47:13.539 --> 47:14.540
I told you she didn't.

47:19.462 --> 47:21.213
She never released the arrow.

47:22.965 --> 47:24.132
What?

47:40.024 --> 47:41.233
She never crossed the line.

47:46.989 --> 47:50.784
My eyes are fried.

47:50.785 --> 47:52.369
He must've been
super diligent.

47:52.370 --> 47:55.413
Never going to the convenience store
across the street.

47:55.414 --> 47:56.540
My thoughts exactly.

47:57.833 --> 47:59.085
Wait.

47:59.668 --> 48:00.920
I think this is him.

48:01.670 --> 48:02.754
Take a look at this.

48:04.924 --> 48:06.967
- It's him, right?
-  Yeah, it is.

48:14.433 --> 48:15.518
Castle Pay!

48:17.395 --> 48:19.020
- Yeah, he used Castle Pay!
- He did.

48:19.021 --> 48:20.772
Good job!

48:20.773 --> 48:21.981
Hold on.

48:21.982 --> 48:26.237
But the CEO of Castle Card is
Senior Managing Director Seong, isn't it?

48:28.781 --> 48:30.824
Let me get this straight.

48:30.825 --> 48:34.703
You need help from your dear brother.

48:35.746 --> 48:37.581
Yes.

48:41.419 --> 48:42.461
I mean, sure.

48:44.171 --> 48:45.755
I could do that for you, but--

48:45.756 --> 48:47.049
Who is he anyway?

48:48.217 --> 48:49.677
He's trying to kill me.

48:52.930 --> 48:53.931
This kid…

48:54.473 --> 48:57.142
Do you take me for a sucker?

48:57.143 --> 48:58.185
Are you serious?

49:01.439 --> 49:03.399
So show me what you can do.

49:04.400 --> 49:06.359
I want some vigilante justice.

49:06.360 --> 49:07.570
This kid…

49:08.988 --> 49:10.406
Who is this guy anyway?

49:30.468 --> 49:31.677
Then do it with me.

49:32.887 --> 49:34.930
Just marry me instead.

49:45.774 --> 49:47.943
Why would I marry you?

49:54.450 --> 49:55.534
Why not?

49:57.161 --> 49:58.662
It's not like you have feelings

49:59.371 --> 50:00.831
for either of us.

50:02.416 --> 50:03.834
You have a five-year term.

50:05.127 --> 50:08.463
It doesn't matter
if I mess up or divorce him.

50:08.464 --> 50:10.007
He'll be a royal for life.

50:10.633 --> 50:11.800
But you're different.

50:17.556 --> 50:18.933
You should serve another term.

50:19.808 --> 50:21.101
Pull yourself together.
:cue

50:53.467 --> 50:54.969
Is it weighing on your mind?

50:58.889 --> 51:00.349
I heard from Aide Choi.

51:00.849 --> 51:03.352
That there was an argument
at your private residence.

51:04.770 --> 51:06.772
Choi Hyeon…

51:07.565 --> 51:09.065
He can be quite the chatterbox.

51:09.066 --> 51:11.360
Just let her win if you can.

51:12.236 --> 51:14.113
She is already under the cutting scrutiny

51:14.613 --> 51:16.155
of the court of public opinion.

51:44.643 --> 51:47.021
PRINCE

51:58.532 --> 51:59.533
Hello.

52:00.826 --> 52:02.328
The invitation
has already been sent.

52:04.788 --> 52:05.956
So you cannot decline.

52:13.881 --> 52:14.965
It's for your sake.

52:17.885 --> 52:18.886
I know.

52:28.771 --> 52:29.813
I'm sorry.

52:31.231 --> 52:33.817
I never meant to hurt you.

52:35.903 --> 52:37.363
Or the cat.

52:38.781 --> 52:39.782
I know.

52:44.953 --> 52:45.954
I'm sorry too.

52:51.085 --> 52:52.336
For not keeping my promise.

52:59.176 --> 53:00.302
As long as you know.

53:13.482 --> 53:15.943
CASTLE BEAUTY

53:24.576 --> 53:26.745
I heard you will be attending.

53:27.579 --> 53:31.666
Yes, well, he just insisted
it would be in my best interest.

53:33.377 --> 53:35.378
There's one thing you should be aware of.

53:35.379 --> 53:37.256
- Just a moment.
- Sure.

53:38.090 --> 53:39.757
- Please continue.
- All right.

53:39.758 --> 53:43.595
All the other invited guests
hold official rank.

53:44.179 --> 53:47.306
In the royal court,
rank defines one's place in the hierarchy.

53:47.307 --> 53:49.727
- Hierarchy?
- Yes. Uh…

53:50.310 --> 53:54.731
I'm sure you noticed
after attending a few royal events.

53:54.732 --> 53:56.899
When you're with someone of a higher rank,

53:56.900 --> 54:00.779
you must walk behind them.
That's the custom.

54:06.118 --> 54:07.202
I'll keep that in mind.

54:08.912 --> 54:10.288
Thank you.

54:10.289 --> 54:11.457
And there's this.

54:12.750 --> 54:13.792
Here.

54:14.501 --> 54:18.254
The first half is a smaller gathering
where the Queen Mother

54:18.255 --> 54:19.589
and the guests mingle.

54:19.590 --> 54:21.090
The second half is a ball.

54:21.091 --> 54:22.634
They call it an "after-party,"

54:23.218 --> 54:27.096
but with the guests' partners,
Cabinet members, and royal family members

54:27.097 --> 54:30.141
all attending,
it's larger in scale than the first part.

54:30.142 --> 54:32.643
I read an article about this
while studying abroad.

54:32.644 --> 54:33.978
You wear gowns and dance…

54:33.979 --> 54:35.396
That's correct.

54:35.397 --> 54:38.484
Then what will Ms. Seong's rank be?

54:40.903 --> 54:43.279
Her rank…

54:43.280 --> 54:47.825
Ms. Seong is super accomplished and all,

54:47.826 --> 54:49.411
but she has no official rank.

54:50.496 --> 54:51.830
- What?
- Well…

54:52.623 --> 54:54.957
She's neither a public official

54:54.958 --> 54:56.876
nor a noble.

54:56.877 --> 55:00.755
So Ms. Seong will be sitting
at the very back of the room

55:00.756 --> 55:02.382
and will always be last in line.

55:03.008 --> 55:07.137
:cue

55:11.058 --> 55:14.520
I would be in front of the line
if I were married, right?

55:25.072 --> 55:27.323
"The attendees receive
honorary decorations

55:27.324 --> 55:31.077
from the royal family
and gain the privilege

55:31.078 --> 55:34.247
of accompanying the court
when it hosts diplomatic events,

55:34.248 --> 55:36.500
starting with the year they are invited."

55:38.085 --> 55:42.130
It is a relief that
I will never have to teach you.

55:45.008 --> 55:47.427
As if she'd ever grant me such privileges.

55:53.058 --> 55:54.560
PRINCE

55:57.062 --> 55:58.063
Hello?

56:00.566 --> 56:01.567
Right now?

56:12.786 --> 56:14.037
What's this about?

56:24.172 --> 56:25.173
Why not?

56:25.674 --> 56:27.383
This will be the last time.

56:28.760 --> 56:32.221
Where did you ever find
the nerve to wear that cheollik?

56:32.222 --> 56:34.349
Was that just a stylistic choice?

56:34.891 --> 56:36.727
I'm doing all this for your sake…

56:52.534 --> 56:53.702
What are you doing?

56:54.328 --> 56:56.288
Don't mind me. Just practicing.

56:57.080 --> 56:59.708
- Practicing what?
- Walking according to rank.

57:00.834 --> 57:04.462
I'll definitely end up walking ahead
that day if I don't practice now.

57:04.463 --> 57:06.673
Because I'm always a trendsetter,
leading the way.

57:31.657 --> 57:34.743
- A word, please!
- Please look over here!

57:36.536 --> 57:39.706
- Over here!
- Give us a pose!

57:44.378 --> 57:47.464
I trust all the preparations are in order?

57:48.090 --> 57:49.675
Yes, Your Majesty.

58:14.282 --> 58:15.575
Bye.

58:17.202 --> 58:18.203
Wait.

58:20.872 --> 58:21.873
"Leading the way."

58:23.041 --> 58:24.209
How do you do it?

58:29.005 --> 58:30.048
I just never learned.

58:31.174 --> 58:33.719
I was always the one following behind.

58:39.683 --> 58:41.184
You just need to walk by my side.

58:43.145 --> 58:44.271
I'll teach you.

59:06.626 --> 59:10.296
Now that Dano, when yang energy is said
to be at its peak, has passed,

59:10.297 --> 59:12.715
the Inner Court Banquet
has finally commenced.

59:12.716 --> 59:14.592
It's a gathering of 20 young women

59:14.593 --> 59:17.595
centered around the Queen Mother,
the head of the Inner Court.

59:17.596 --> 59:20.681
This year's guest list includes
Seong Huiju, CEO of Castle Beauty,

59:20.682 --> 59:22.017
drawing significant attention.

59:22.851 --> 59:25.019
-  Babe!
- You scared me.

59:25.020 --> 59:26.271
Babe.

59:27.647 --> 59:29.232
I found the punk who rigged her car.

59:30.484 --> 59:31.817
You did?

59:31.818 --> 59:33.153
Yeah, but…

59:33.862 --> 59:34.905
But?

59:35.822 --> 59:36.990
He's dead.

59:37.574 --> 59:39.326
- What?
- He died.

59:39.951 --> 59:40.952
Yesterday.
:cue

59:43.163 --> 59:45.122
JUNIOR 4TH RANK, SENIOR 4TH RANK

59:45.123 --> 59:46.665
JUNIOR 5TH RANK

59:51.588 --> 59:52.671
JUNIOR 6TH RANK

59:52.672 --> 59:54.173
SEONG HUIJU, COMMONER

59:54.174 --> 59:56.509
For all her much-touted success abroad,

59:56.510 --> 59:58.302
she was never invited.

59:58.303 --> 01:00:00.346
It seems being the Grand Prince's woman

01:00:00.347 --> 01:00:02.932
outweighs any barrier of status.

01:00:02.933 --> 01:00:05.518
If she successfully marries him,
she will be royalty,

01:00:05.519 --> 01:00:07.561
so they must be keeping up appearances.

01:00:07.562 --> 01:00:09.230
Even so,

01:00:09.231 --> 01:00:11.274
is she not someone
who caused a public scandal?

01:00:11.900 --> 01:00:13.943
If she had been a guest last year,

01:00:13.944 --> 01:00:16.696
at least they could have used
her achievements as an excuse.

01:00:17.656 --> 01:00:20.032
The royal family is such a joke
these days.

01:00:22.953 --> 01:00:24.621
- Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

01:00:25.580 --> 01:00:26.915
SEONG HUIJU, COMMONER

01:00:29.960 --> 01:00:32.336
Were you speaking ill
of someone who is not even here?

01:00:32.337 --> 01:00:34.840
Pardon?

01:00:35.423 --> 01:00:36.883
I should have come later.

01:00:37.884 --> 01:00:39.135
Considering you saw fit

01:00:39.886 --> 01:00:41.805
to drag the royal family into your gossip.

01:00:42.597 --> 01:00:44.223
Ms. Seong, over here!

01:00:44.224 --> 01:00:47.059
- Ms. Seong, over here!
- Please look here!

01:01:01.908 --> 01:01:03.285
Your Majesty.

01:01:04.327 --> 01:01:05.995
I am Huiju of the Seong Family.

01:01:05.996 --> 01:01:07.496
-  Ms. Seong.
-  Ms. Seong!

01:01:07.497 --> 01:01:10.499
How does it feel to be back
at the palace since going public?

01:01:10.500 --> 01:01:12.418
What was the palace's stance
on the accident?

01:01:12.419 --> 01:01:15.212
Is there a reason
why you arrived after Her Majesty?

01:01:15.213 --> 01:01:17.047
-  Please give us a comment!
-  Please!

01:01:17.048 --> 01:01:19.091
- We await your response.
- Give us a comment.

01:01:19.092 --> 01:01:21.678
Unfortunately, I still do not know
my way around the palace.

01:01:22.345 --> 01:01:25.472
I ended up losing my way for a moment.

01:01:30.437 --> 01:01:32.230
Please forgive me,

01:01:32.939 --> 01:01:33.982
Your Majesty.

01:01:42.407 --> 01:01:45.035
I was told the Royal Secretariat
provided you with guidance.

01:01:46.202 --> 01:01:48.705
Did you avoid wearing a dangui
for some particular reason?

01:01:49.664 --> 01:01:50.749
Ah!

01:01:51.583 --> 01:01:55.086
I was led to believe
that custom was not mandatory.

01:01:58.423 --> 01:02:00.257
Is it not to your liking?

01:02:05.597 --> 01:02:06.598
How could it not be?

01:02:16.942 --> 01:02:20.403
-  Would you care to respond?
-  Ms. Seong, over here.

01:02:29.120 --> 01:02:31.705
The snacks Your Majesty sent
for Children's Day

01:02:31.706 --> 01:02:35.793
brought great joy to all the patients
in the pediatric ward.

01:02:35.794 --> 01:02:38.213
I am more than happy
to help in any way I can.

01:02:38.838 --> 01:02:41.341
Do not hesitate to let me know.

01:02:41.967 --> 01:02:45.010
I heard Your Majesty enjoyed
my performances.

01:02:45.011 --> 01:02:48.348
If Your Majesty could attend the next one,
I would be greatly honored…

01:02:58.984 --> 01:03:00.609
Perhaps the summer is to thank,

01:03:00.610 --> 01:03:03.904
but do you not find the palace grounds
even more beautiful?

01:03:03.905 --> 01:03:05.031
Pardon?

01:03:05.699 --> 01:03:07.117
Yes, Your Majesty.

01:03:08.076 --> 01:03:09.369
Let us walk a bit longer.

01:03:09.869 --> 01:03:12.872
When the flowers are in bloom,
appreciating them is one's duty.

01:03:13.456 --> 01:03:15.166
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

01:04:07.177 --> 01:04:08.636
Please teach me.

01:04:10.722 --> 01:04:11.973
Now that I am by your side.

01:04:13.808 --> 01:04:15.810
:cue

01:04:52.013 --> 01:04:53.181
Do not bend to their will.

01:04:54.933 --> 01:04:55.934
Do not step back

01:04:56.851 --> 01:04:58.103
and do not compromise.

01:05:00.188 --> 01:05:01.731
I shall fight with all that I have.

01:05:06.861 --> 01:05:07.862
Just as you do.

01:05:22.919 --> 01:05:25.921
PERFECT CROWN

01:06:01.916 --> 01:06:05.002
From when you were
just acquaintances to now,

01:06:05.003 --> 01:06:06.795
what would you say is the biggest change?

01:06:06.796 --> 01:06:08.422
Being overprotective?

01:06:08.423 --> 01:06:09.423
That's a bit too naive, no?

01:06:09.424 --> 01:06:13.469
A businesswoman should know better
than to trust people so easily.

01:06:14.053 --> 01:06:15.555
There's a spy at my private residence.

01:06:16.222 --> 01:06:17.472
Seong Huiju!

01:06:17.473 --> 01:06:20.185
Don't you find him to be so impatient?

01:06:22.353 --> 01:06:23.729
Your Royal Highness?

01:06:23.730 --> 01:06:25.814
Will you give me your hand in marriage?

01:06:25.815 --> 01:06:27.941
Did you think
I would simply let this stand?

01:06:27.942 --> 01:06:29.151
Announce me.

01:06:29.152 --> 01:06:31.988
How could I refuse a request
from the Queen Mother?

01:06:33.198 --> 01:06:35.074
You should only have eyes for me.

01:06:35.575 --> 01:06:37.911
As if we were hopelessly in love.

01:06:45.043 --> 01:06:52.050
EPILOGUE

01:06:55.720 --> 01:06:57.722
Oh!

01:07:12.862 --> 01:07:13.863
Wait.

01:07:15.573 --> 01:07:16.574
You…

01:07:20.370 --> 01:07:21.454
You did well

01:07:22.413 --> 01:07:23.748
during the exhibition match.

01:07:26.876 --> 01:07:29.879
Are you trying to take credit?

01:07:32.966 --> 01:07:34.091
"Take credit"?

01:07:34.092 --> 01:07:36.219
Do you not grasp
the concept of a compliment?

01:07:38.596 --> 01:07:39.639
I guess not.

01:08:12.922 --> 01:08:14.465
Darn it, you scared me.

01:08:15.550 --> 01:08:16.968
Have you been there?

01:08:17.510 --> 01:08:18.636
- Yes.
- Since when?

01:08:19.887 --> 01:08:21.722
Before you started lingering.

01:08:35.194 --> 01:08:37.238
Are you close to Seong Huiju?

01:08:39.949 --> 01:08:41.993
We're close.
We live in the same dorms too.

01:08:43.286 --> 01:08:44.495
What is she like?

01:08:52.128 --> 01:08:53.338
She's pretty.

01:08:55.340 --> 01:08:56.632
Yeah, she is.

01:09:08.895 --> 01:09:10.979
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:09:22.241 --> 01:09:25.912
PERFECT CROWN
